<p><em><strong>10. <a href="http://www.slashfilm.com/new-kids-turbo-penumbra-minireviews-fantastic-fest-2011/" target="_blank">New Kids Turbo</a></strong></em> – The biggest box office hit in the history of The Netherlands, <em>New Kids Turbo</em> is lewd, crude comedy with a social message and characters that grow on you to a point you don’t want the movie to end.</p>
