		<title>Reshoots Changed Original Ending of ‘Rise of the Planet of the Apes’</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/slashfilm/~3/Jwv7OCWul-0/</link>
		<comments>http://www.slashfilm.com/reshoots-changed-original-planet-rise-apes/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 03 Oct 2011 16:30:59 +0000</pubDate>
