		<title>‘Star Trek 2′ Update: Location Scout Underway, Comics Will ‘Foreshadow’ Film</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/slashfilm/~3/TRy8wOo6onc/</link>
		<comments>http://www.slashfilm.com/star-trek-2-update-location-scout-underway-comics-foreshadow-film/#comments</comments>
