		<title>‘Green Lantern’ Co-Writer Marc Guggenheim Developing Sci-Fi Fantasy ‘Time Zones’ for Disney</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/slashfilm/~3/Yxyq_sXDJ08/</link>
		<comments>http://www.slashfilm.com/green-lantern-cowriter-marc-guggenheim-developing-scifi-fantasy-time-zones-disney/#comments</comments>
